            <mn>10</mn>
          </mrow>
        </msup>
      </mstyle>
    </mrow>
    <annotation encoding=3D"application/x-tex">{\displaystyle 10^{10}}</ann=
otation>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src=3D"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/rend=
er/svg/b086010e3cc3b0a4e22c858243d32ec1cc648e6a" class=3D"mwe-math-fallback=
-image-inline mw-invert skin-invert" aria-hidden=3D"true" style=3D"vertical=
-align: -0.338ex; width:4.201ex; height:2.676ex;" alt=3D"{\displaystyle 10^=
{10}}"></span> and <span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"=
><span class=3D"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"displ=
ay: none;"><math xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext=3D"{\=
displaystyle 10^{9}}">
  <semantics>
    <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
      <mstyle displaystyle=3D"true" scriptlevel=3D"0">
        <msup>
          <mn>10</mn>
          <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
            <mn>9</mn>
          </mrow>
        </msup>
      </mstyle>
    </mrow>
    <annotation encoding=3D"application/x-tex">{\displaystyle 10^{9}}</anno=
tation>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src=3D"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/rend=
er/svg/c5f8dddd44eb018f09163e18ba8f19485e38bdb7" class=3D"mwe-math-fallback=
-image-inline mw-invert skin-invert" aria-hidden=3D"true" style=3D"vertical=
-align: -0.338ex; width:3.379ex; height:2.676ex;" alt=3D"{\displaystyle 10^=
{9}}"></span></dd></dl>
<p>The relative error is
</p>
<dl><dd><span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span clas=
s=3D"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none;">=
<math xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext=3D"{\displaystyl=
e 1-{\frac {10^{9}}{10^{10}}}=3D1-{\frac {1}{10}}=3D90\%}">
  <semantics>
    <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
      <mstyle displaystyle=3D"true" scriptlevel=3D"0">
        <mn>1</mn>
        <mo>=E2=88=92<!-- =E2=88=92 --></mo>
        <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
          <mfrac>
            <msup>
              <mn>10</mn>
              <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
                <mn>9</mn>
              </mrow>
            </msup>
            <msup>
              <mn>10</mn>
              <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
                <mn>10</mn>
              </mrow>
            </msup>
          </mfrac>
        </mrow>
        <mo>=3D</mo>
        <mn>1</mn>
        <mo>=E2=88=92<!-- =E2=88=92 --></mo>
        <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
          <mfrac>
            <mn>1</mn>
            <mn>10</mn>
          </mfrac>
        </mrow>
        <mo>=3D</mo>
        <mn>90</mn>
        <mi mathvariant=3D"normal">%<!-- % --></mi>
      </mstyle>
    </mrow>
    <annotation encoding=3D"application/x-tex">{\displaystyle 1-{\frac {10^=
{9}}{10^{10}}}=3D1-{\frac {1}{10}}=3D90\%}</annotation>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src=3D"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/rend=
er/svg/5bf1fbe2253cd06911ab6724eb51689232c1e132" class=3D"mwe-math-fallback=
-image-inline mw-invert skin-invert" aria-hidden=3D"true" style=3D"vertical=
-align: -2.338ex; width:26.662ex; height:6.176ex;" alt=3D"{\displaystyle 1-=
{\frac {10^{9}}{10^{10}}}=3D1-{\frac {1}{10}}=3D90\%}"></span></dd></dl>
<p>a large relative error. However, one can also consider the relative erro=
r in the logarithms; in this case, the logarithms (to base 10) are 10 and 9=
, so the relative error in the logarithms is only 10%.
</p><p>The point is that <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Exponenti=
al_function" title=3D"Exponential function">exponential functions</a> magni=
fy relative errors greatly =E2=80=93 if <i>a</i> and <i>b</i> have a small =
relative error,
</p>
<dl><dd><span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span clas=
s=3D"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none;">=
<math xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext=3D"{\displaystyl=
e 10^{a}}">
  <semantics>
    <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
      <mstyle displaystyle=3D"true" scriptlevel=3D"0">
        <msup>
          <mn>10</mn>
          <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
            <mi>a</mi>
          </mrow>
        </msup>
      </mstyle>
    </mrow>
    <annotation encoding=3D"application/x-tex">{\displaystyle 10^{a}}</anno=
tation>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src=3D"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/rend=
er/svg/435cc45764ed96d41ebe48fa56d042a4c93bc3ea" class=3D"mwe-math-fallback=
-image-inline mw-invert skin-invert" aria-hidden=3D"true" style=3D"vertical=
