    </mrow>
    <annotation encoding=3D"application/x-tex">{\displaystyle 10^{10^{b}}}<=
/annotation>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src=3D"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/rend=
er/svg/c1aae830076b4f6de7ac7b885dfa1c963f422f7c" class=3D"mwe-math-fallback=
-image-inline mw-invert skin-invert" aria-hidden=3D"true" style=3D"vertical=
