er">transfinite numbers</a>. For example, <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.o=
rg/wiki/Aleph-null" class=3D"mw-redirect" title=3D"Aleph-null">aleph-null</=
a> is the <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cardinality" title=3D"Ca=
