/en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Natural_number" title=3D"Natural number">natural num=
bers</a>, and <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Aleph-one" class=3D"=
mw-redirect" title=3D"Aleph-one">aleph-one</a> is the next greatest cardina=
l number. <span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span cl=
